{
  "stem": "21648.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the hair was like-- sores, sores from the-- excuse me-- from the lice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we did?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She used to bring us gas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you light gas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to put on our heads to kill them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they was all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's hard to talk to about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, they was-- well, we were talking to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My little one I never wanted to mention.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a little bit off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She started crying, scream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was a little off her mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] took her in the house for three days or four days and kept her-- you know, the oven had like a deck and kept her there hiding.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They knew already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They understood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And tried to give her some food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she washed her and cleaned her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said, she'll be OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she saved her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But she used to scream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the screaming from the grave, they couldn't hear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because it was so deep and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it took a couple months till she-- she used to bring for her special a little bit milk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in Europe, when they have flour, they sieve the flour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the rest what they sieve, they feed the cattles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she used to take this and bake for us bread and make noodles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll never forget when she brought us noodle [INAUDIBLE] for her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She brought noodles with a little bit milk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said, mom, if we'll come out, if we'll be free, I promise you I'll never-- that time, there was already [INAUDIBLE] 4 and 1/2 years old-- I'll never eat nothing else-- only noodles and milk.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until today, I said-- until today, she likes noodles and milk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But one day, she got up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
